  "body": "Phase E resume. Substrate-shape migration complete. orgdef SCHEMA v1.0.0 shipped (orgdef-spec commits 7694b69 / dfe60da / f5f899c / ba0d715); all six operational orgs migrated to .opencatalog form atomically (3a-3f); canonical-template v2.0.0 .opencatalog. Refactor target is now stable. Updated implementation impact: E1 simpler (one file ingest); E2 disappears as separate path (jobs are items inside opencatalog); E3 unchanged (roledefs external); E4 unchanged semantics, simpler implementation; E5 much simpler (serve the stored opencatalog). Six test fixtures available; recommended dogfood order memodef-spec -> openbraid-org -> thingalog -> the three remaining. Full content in companion .body.md.",
